text: Lucía Vaamonde is a hurdler from Venezuela. Vaamonde competed at the 1972 Summer Olympics and the 1976 Summer Olympics. She was born on 13 December 1949.Lucía Vaamonde == References == Category:1949 births Category:Living people Category:Venezuelan athletes Category:Hurdlers Category:Olympians for Venezuela
